  "description": "Covaplus Vinyl Matt Johnstone's Trade Covaplus Vinyl Matt is a high-quality matt emulsion, suitable for all interior walls and ceilings, providing excellent opacity, coverage and application. Ideal for use on wood, metal and plaster as well as wallboards, concrete, cement rendering, brickwork and blockwork in internal situations, our Covaplus Vinyl Matt is available in thousands of colours via the Johnstone's Tinting System. Johnstone's Trade Covaplus Vinyl Matt will cover approximately 12-14 square metres per litre, depending on the nature and porosity of the surface being painted, and is touch dry in 1-2 hours and recoatable after 2-4 hours. USE ON - Interior SUBSTRATE - Blockwork, Brickwork, Cement Render, Concrete, Plaster, Wallboards APPLICATION - Brush, Roller and Spray FINISH - Matt TYPE - Water Based RECOAT - 2-4 Hours COVERAGE - 12-14 sqm / Litre",
